## One-Line Terminal Tests

```js
require("./index.js").tiktok("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").photooxy("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").textpro("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").glowtext({}).then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").insta_reel("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").insta_post("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").insta_story("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").insta_profile("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").npm_user("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").npm_module("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").github_user("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").system_requirements("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").gpu_scraper("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
require("./index.js").similarity("", "").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
// Artbreeder cannot useable in node command prompt.

// require("./index.js").function("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
// require("./index.js").function("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})
// require("./index.js").function("").then(async(test)=>{console.log(test)})

process.exit() // Exit The Promises
```

## Promise 
```js
require("./index.js").function("")
```

```js
Promise {
  <pending>,
  [Symbol(async_id_symbol)]: id, // Number
  [Symbol(trigger_async_id_symbol)]: id, // Number
  [Symbol(destroyed)]: { destroyed: false } // Boolean
}
```
